{"type":"message","id":"d6d344b4","parentId":"d7f8d639","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:42:55.850Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我在 2026.3.8 版本的 changelog 中没有找到直接关于 `EnvironmentFile` 被移除的记录。但从文件 stat 信息来看，service 文件是在 2026-03-10 04:10:46 修改的，这正好是 gateway 从 v2026.3.7 升级到 v2026.3.8 的时候。\n\n让我查看 openclaw 源码中生成 systemd service 文件的逻辑，看看 `EnvironmentFile` 是如何处理的。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4905e9e561d44e982f1f298","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -B20 -A40 \"EnvironmentFile\\|buildSystemdUnit\" ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/systemd-D6iXPkQu.js | head -150"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773117771574}}
